{"words":[{"word":"seaside","count":4},{"word":"arena","count":4},{"word":"rover","count":4},{"word":"strength","count":3},{"word":"i'll","count":3},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"factions","count":3},{"word":"freedom","count":3},{"word":"take","count":2},{"word":"last","count":2},{"word":"maybe","count":2},{"word":"participants","count":2},{"word":"high-ranked","count":2},{"word":"hope","count":2},{"word":"help","count":2},{"word":"regain","count":2},{"word":"trap","count":2},{"word":"set","count":2},{"word":"into","count":2},{"word":"answer","count":2},{"word":"lost","count":2},{"word":"fulfill","count":2},{"word":"faction","count":2},{"word":"camp","count":2},{"word":"badge","count":1},{"word":"indeed","count":1},{"word":"strong","count":1},{"word":"forge","count":1},{"word":"report","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"hone","count":1},{"word":"skills","count":1},{"word":"frank","count":1},{"word":"steering","count":1},{"word":"wheel","count":1},{"word":"held","count":1},{"word":"ensure","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"top","count":1},{"word":"leaderboard","count":1},{"word":"rule","count":1},{"word":"tactics","count":1},{"word":"maintain","count":1},{"word":"positions","count":1},{"word":"three","count":1},{"word":"trials","count":1},{"word":"passed","count":1},{"word":"screen","count":1},{"word":"unqualified","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"precisely","count":1},{"word":"assess","count":1},{"word":"gathering","count":1},{"word":"information","count":1},{"word":"case","count":1},{"word":"well-prepared","count":1},{"word":"official","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"examiners","count":1},{"word":"responsible","count":1},{"word":"submitting","count":1},{"word":"assessment","count":1},{"word":"reports","count":1},{"word":"believe","count":1},{"word":"honestly","count":1},{"word":"challenger","count":1},{"word":"however","count":1},{"word":"obsession","count":1},{"word":"victory","count":1},{"word":"led","count":1},{"word":"lose","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1},{"word":"discovered","count":1},{"word":"waiting","count":1},{"word":"innocent","count":1},{"word":"jump","count":1},{"word":"survival-of-the-fittest","count":1},{"word":"world","count":1},{"word":"speaks","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"power","count":1},{"word":"change","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"countless","count":1},{"word":"challengers","count":1},{"word":"keen","count":1},{"word":"observation","count":1},{"word":"resort","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"another","count":1},{"word":"merely","count":1},{"word":"bided","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"pointed","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"pretext","count":1},{"word":"exploiting","count":1},{"word":"vulnerable","count":1},{"word":"completely","count":1},{"word":"integrity","count":1},{"word":"devolved","count":1},{"word":"means","count":1},{"word":"insatiable","count":1},{"word":"greed","count":1},{"word":"refuse","count":1},{"word":"manipulated","count":1},{"word":"mere","count":1},{"word":"puppet","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"promise","count":1},{"word":"according","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"winner","count":1},{"word":"memory","count":1},{"word":"serves","count":1},{"word":"received","count":1},{"word":"assistance","count":1},{"word":"hyenas","count":1},{"word":"correct","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"naivety","count":1},{"word":"attained","count":1},{"word":"current","count":1},{"word":"status","count":1},{"word":"add","count":1},{"word":"additional","count":1},{"word":"condition","count":1},{"word":"defeated","count":1},{"word":"party","count":1},{"word":"publicly","count":1},{"word":"declare","count":1},{"word":"victor's","count":1},{"word":"terms","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"center","count":1},{"word":"catch","count":1},{"word":"shortly","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Take it. It's the last badge. You're indeed strong.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"With your strength, maybe... I'll forge a report just like they do this time.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Do you new participants really think the Seaside Arena is a place for you to hone your skills?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"To be frank with you, the Seaside Arena is now a steering wheel held by those high-ranked factions.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"They can ensure they're always at the top of the leaderboard. Even this rule is one of their tactics to maintain their positions.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"The three trials you just passed not only screen out the unqualified but also give them a chance to precisely assess the strength of the participants, gathering information.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"In this case, they can be well-prepared in the official match. And, we examiners are responsible for submitting the assessment reports to those factions.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Because I see hope in you. I think you can help me regain my freedom.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Believe it or not. Honestly, I see hope in you. I think you can help me regain my freedom.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"I was once a challenger in the Seaside Arena. However, my obsession with victory led me to lose my own freedom.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Later, I discovered it was a trap set by those high-ranked factions, waiting for the innocent to jump into it.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"In this survival-of-the-fittest world, only strength speaks.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"I no longer have the power to change it, but maybe you can. I've seen countless challengers, and I have keen observation.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Will you be my last resort?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"No need to think about it. Rover must has {Male=his;Female=her} own answer.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"It's just another trap set by you. Am I right?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"I merely bided my time for the right moment. As Rover pointed out, it's nothing more than your pretext for exploiting the vulnerable.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"The Seaside Arena has completely lost its integrity. It has devolved into a means to fulfill your insatiable greed. I refuse to be manipulated like a mere puppet.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Since you've lost, it's time to fulfill your promise according to the rules.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Rover, you're the winner, so it's up to you to answer.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"If my memory serves me right, your faction received assistance from The Hyenas, correct?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Without such naivety, would your faction have attained its current status?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Rover, can you add an additional condition?","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Have the defeated party publicly declare the victor's terms to everyone in the camp.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005},{"text":"Alright, I'll take him to the center of the camp. I'll catch up with you shortly.","quest_name":"A True Arena Champion","quest_id":135000005}]}